    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>yellow mustard seeds</strong>, <strong>cumin seeds </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> and roughly grind until the seeds are starting to break down – this is your <strong>ground spice mix</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>ground spice mix </strong>to the pan with the <strong>ground paprika</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric </strong>and <strong>ground coriander </strong>and cook for a further 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
