        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roughly chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and <strong>chopped creamed</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>in 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with the <strong>tamarind paste </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato coconut stock</strong></p>",
