      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato coconut stock </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to thicken – this is your <strong>curry sauce</strong></p>",
