      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>haddock bites </strong>into even, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Once slightly thickened, add the <strong>chopped haddock</strong> to the curry sauce and cook, covered, for 4-5 min further or until the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>Zanzibar-style haddock & pepper curry</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
