    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Zanzibar-style haddock & pepper curry</strong> over the <strong>cooked rice</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
